      "orig": "An Entropy Oriented Trading strategy has n target types of asset A 0 , · · · , A n -1 . It has constant weights for the assets ( w 0 , w 1 , · · · , w n -1 ), where the weights are positive and the sum of them is one. The price and the held amount of the i th asset are written as p i and h i respectively. The value of the i th asset is",
